						<summary>

						<p>On pillar No. 8 in the compound of the Taluk Office.</p>						

						<p>The record is in verse and undated. Written in characters of 12th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>Records a gift of 2 <hi rend="italic">puṭṭis</hi> of land at Kannaripūṁḍi near Bhīmavrōlu for maintaining 12 lamps in the temple of Bhīmēśvara by Maṁgūri Annaya.</p>						

